svg.title: Artboard 1
svg.text: John is a operator working for Intelligent Traffic system. He has been monitoring human driven vehicle and would asist the driver from the remote location. He would convey the traffic conditions, help in vehicle breakdown, etc. Now he has to work with self driven autonomus vehicle. He is looking for a platform thorugh which he can do same funcinalities without any errors and quickly.
-Monitor vehicle-View map, routes, vehicles, infrastructure items, notifications
-Addressing issue remotely-Lot of things to monitor-Difficult to view object’s status
